Rodd Redwing https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rodd_Redwing 0 Rodd Redwing, also known as Roderic Redwing or Rodric Redwing (August 24, 1904 – May 29, 1971), claimed to be a Native American actor and was noted as a quick-draw artist with six-guns. Recent research on Redwing shows that in the United States Census 1940, his birthplace was listed as India and not New York City. Other sources say his real name was Roderick Rajpurkaii Jr. Rodd_Redwing , also_known as Roderic_Redwing or Rodric_Redwing ( August_24_,_1904 – May_29_,_1971 ) , claimed_to_be a_Native_American_actor and was_noted as a_quick-draw_artist with six-guns .
